## Next Steps

To connect this to your Python backend:
1.  Update [src/services/api.js](file:///c:/HelioX/frontend/src/services/api.js) to replace the [submitQuery](file:///c:/HelioX/frontend/src/services/api.js#8-99) mock with an actual `fetch` or `axios` POST request to your FastAPI endpoint.
2.  Ensure your FastAPI application enables CORS for `http://localhost:5173`.
